==English==
===Noun===
'''flagship'''

# In a [[maritime]] fleet, the ship occupied by the fleet's captain; it denotes this by flying the captain's flag.

===Adjective===
'''flagship'''

# An evolved word from the noun above, used to refer to the most important item out of a selection, e.g. ''the retail company's flagship store in the city''.

